{"id":599,"parent_id":497,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":599,"title":"Psalm 102","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ps.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Psalm 102"],[".studySummary",["i","The psalmist offers a prayer of the afflicted—Zion will be built up when the Lord appears in His glory—Though the heaven and earth perish, the Lord who created them will endure forever."]],[".intro","A Prayer of the afflicted, when he is overwhelmed, and poureth out his complaint before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.1","order":"02.20.102.39120"},["b","1"],"Hear my prayer, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and let my cry come unto thee."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.2","order":"02.20.102.39121"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Hide"],"not thy face from me in the day",["i","when"],"I am in trouble; incline thine ear unto me: in the day",["i","when"],"I call answer me speedily."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.3","order":"02.20.102.39122"},["b","3"],"For my days are consumed like smoke, and my bones are burned as an hearth."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.4","order":"02.20.102.39123"},["b","4"],"My heart is smitten, and withered like grass; so that I forget to eat my bread."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.5","order":"02.20.102.39124"},["b","5"],"By reason of the voice of my groaning my bones cleave to my skin."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.6","order":"02.20.102.39125"},["b","6"],"I am like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"pelican"],"of the wilderness: I am like an owl of the desert."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.7","order":"02.20.102.39126"},["b","7"],"I watch, and am as a sparrow alone upon the house top."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.8","order":"02.20.102.39127"},["b","8"],"Mine enemies reproach me all the day;",["i","and"],"they that are mad against me are sworn against me."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.9","order":"02.20.102.39128"},["b","9"],"For I have eaten ashes like bread, and mingled my drink with weeping,"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.10","order":"02.20.102.39129"},["b","10"],"Because of thine indignation and thy wrath: for thou hast lifted me up, and cast me down."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.11","order":"02.20.102.39130"},["b","11"],"My days",["i","are"],"like a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"shadow"],"that declineth; and I am withered like",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"grass"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.12","order":"02.20.102.39131"},["b","12"],"But thou, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", shalt endure for",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"ever"],"; and thy remembrance unto all generations."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.13","order":"02.20.102.39132"},["b","13"],"Thou shalt arise,",["i","and"],"have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"mercy"],"upon",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"Zion"],": for the time to favour her, yea, the set time, is come."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.14","order":"02.20.102.39133"},["b","14"],"For thy servants take pleasure in her stones, and favour the dust thereof."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.15","order":"02.20.102.39134"},["b","15"],"So the heathen shall fear the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and all the kings of the earth thy glory."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.16","order":"02.20.102.39135"},["b","16"],"When the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall build up Zion, he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"appear"],"in his glory."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.17","order":"02.20.102.39136"},["b","17"],"He will regard the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"prayer"],"of the destitute, and not despise their prayer."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.18","order":"02.20.102.39137"},["b","18"],"This shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"written"],"for the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_18b"},"generation"],"to come: and the people which shall be created shall praise the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.19","order":"02.20.102.39138"},["b","19"],"For he hath looked down from the height of his sanctuary; from heaven did the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"behold the earth;"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.20","order":"02.20.102.39139"},["b","20"],"To hear the groaning of the prisoner; to loose those that are appointed to death;"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.21","order":"02.20.102.39140"},["b","21"],"To declare the name of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"in Zion, and his praise in Jerusalem;"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.22","order":"02.20.102.39141"},["b","22"],"When the people are gathered together, and the kingdoms, to serve the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.23","order":"02.20.102.39142"},["b","23"],"He weakened my strength in the way; he shortened my days."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.24","order":"02.20.102.39143"},["b","24"],"I said, O my God, take me not away in the midst of my days: thy years",["i","are"],"throughout all generations."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.25","order":"02.20.102.39144"},["b","25"],"Of old hast thou laid the foundation of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"earth"],": and the heavens",["i","are"],"the work of thy hands."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.26","order":"02.20.102.39145"},["b","26"],"They shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"perish"],", but thou shalt endure: yea, all of them shall wax old like a garment; as a vesture shalt thou change them, and they shall be changed:"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.27","order":"02.20.102.39146"},["b","27"],"But thou",["i","art"],"the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"same"],", and thy years shall have no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"end"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.28","order":"02.20.102.39147"},["b","28"],"The children of thy servants shall continue, and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"seed"],"shall be established before thee."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.2a","order":"02.20.102.39148"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.1.1-8"},"D&C 121:1 (1–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.6a","order":"02.20.102.39150"},["b","6a"],["span.small","HEB"],"vulture, hawk."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.11a","order":"02.20.102.39152"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-chr/29.15"},"1 Chr. 29:15"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/144.4"},"Ps. 144:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.11b","order":"02.20.102.39154"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/40.6.6-8"},"Isa. 40:6 (6–8)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.12a","order":"02.20.102.39156"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/immortality"},"TG Immortality"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.13a","order":"02.20.102.39158"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.1"},"Isa. 14:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.13b","order":"02.20.102.39160"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/zion"},"TG Zion"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.16a","order":"02.20.102.39162"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-second-coming"},"TG Jesus Christ, Second Coming"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.17a","order":"02.20.102.39164"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.37"},"Ezek. 36:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.18a","order":"02.20.102.39166"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."],["div",{"id":"18b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.18b","order":"02.20.102.39168"},["b","18b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/48.13"},"Ps. 48:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.25a","order":"02.20.102.39170"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/creation"},"TG Creation"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.26a","order":"02.20.102.39172"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/34.4"},"Isa. 34:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/51.6"},"51:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.10.10-12"},"2 Pet. 3:10 (10–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.27a","order":"02.20.102.39174"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-eternal-nature-of"},"TG God, Eternal Nature of"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.27b","order":"02.20.102.39176"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/eternity"},"TG Eternity"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ps/102.28a","order":"02.20.102.39178"},["b","28a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/29.14"},"2 Ne. 29:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.30"},"D&C 132:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.52.50-53"},"Moses 7:52 (50–53)"],"."]]}
